nodes.text: A clone trooper was part of a unit led by Jedi General Chiata and her Padawan Marseph. He was assigned to a Venator-class Star Destroyer. After exiting hyperspace, the ship crashed on Zeffo. The clone trooper died in the crash.
The clone trooper wore armor similar to the 13th Battalion led by Jaro Tapal, though with lighter yellow markings.
